                        data-center-center="transform:scale(1.1)",
                        data-top-bottom="transform:scale(1.2)")
                p.repr
                  img(src='/images/otono.png')
                p
                  | Next generation telecom connectivity.
                p.visit
                  a(href="http://otono.com", target="_blank") View App &rsaquo;


